title: Comfortable living. Conveniently located, spacious 1 bed 1 bath!
posting_body: ['Stoneleigh at the Reserve', 'Located at: 5200 Annapolis Ln N Plymouth, MN 55446', 'Featured unit: 1 bed | 1 bath | 720 - 730 sq ft', 'Prices start at: $1445 - $1520/month', 'Call Today!', 'show contact info', "The only thing that rivals Stoneleigh's exceptional property is our premium location that's just 15 miles northwest of Minneapolis.", "Here you'll have easy access to I-494, and a public bus stop is just steps outside our front door.", "The Reserve Park is a five-minute walk down the street: it's a great place to have a picnic, go for a walk, or let the kids run and play.", "Just down the road, you'll find Rockford Road Plaza where you can pick up necessities at Target, grab a quick burger at Five Guys, and discover the latest fashions at Kohl's.", 'Wonderful Amenities!', '➢ Bike Storage', '➢ Coffee Station', '➢ Conference Room', '➢ Elevator', '➢ Fitness Center', '➢ Free Weights', '➢ Gameroom', '➢ Pool', '➢ Recycling', '➢ Resident Lounge', '➢ Barbecue/Grill Area', '➢ Business Center', '➢ Cardio Machines', '➢ Complimentary DVD/Video Rental', '➢ Controlled Access Building', '➢ Disposal Chutes', '➢ On-site Maintenance & Management', '➢ Racquetball Court', '➢ Reserveable Clubhouse', '➢ Wake Up With Weidner Continental Breakfast', 'Apartment Features!', '➢ Air Conditioning', '➢ Dining Room', '➢ Dishwasher', '➢ Full-Size Washer/Dryer in Every Home', '➢ Garbage Disposal', '➢ Linen Closet', '➢ Microwave', '➢ Patio/Balcony In Select Units', '➢ Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', '➢ Walk-In Closets In Select Units', 'show contact info', 'Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 5:00 PM', 'Sun: 12:00 PM - 4:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Terms:', 'Variable', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Fees and deposits apply, please contact the community office for additional information.', '100 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '14C03077AC4348F5']
